OL,3,GNEWSCITV introduces in-game ads for Six
OL,4,CNations
OL,5,
OL,6,FTonight's first match of the 2026 Six
OL,7,FNations rugby will see a first for
OL,8,Fcommercial rugby broadcasting in the
OL,9,FUK.
OL,11,FITV plans to play split-screen
OL,12,Fadvertisements whilst the game is in
OL,13,Fprogress.
OL,15,FOne 20-second ad will be shown during
OL,16,Feach half of the match. The ad will be
OL,17,Fshown on the right-hand side of the
OL,18,Fscreen, whilst live match pictures
OL,19,Fcontinue on the left.
