OL,3,GNEWSCITV introduces in-game ads for Six
OL,4,CNations
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe plan is to run the ads when there
OL,7,Fis a break in play, just before a
OL,8,Fscrum. Samsung and Virgin Atlantic will
OL,9,Fbe the first to trial the new format.
OL,11,FSplit-screen advertising has been part
OL,12,Fof live sport coverage for years in the
OL,13,FUnited States.
OL,15,FRTE has been experimenting with the
OL,16,Fformat during its horse racing
OL,17,Fcoverage.
OL,19,FUPDATE: a lot of negative feedback this
OL,20,Fevening on social media from ITV
OL,21,Fviewers. One to watch.
